snippet: Arsenal wasted a two-goal lead for the second time in a week, with a 3-3 draw against Fulham prolonging the team’s worst Premier League start under Arsene Wenger.
lead_paragraph: Arsenal wasted a two-goal lead for the second time in a week, with a 3-3 draw against Fulham prolonging the team’s worst Premier League start under Arsene Wenger.
